name: Andhika The Seeker
description:
"There is no truth, only facts." So he says to himself whenever he finds himself in a particularly complicated investigation.

His cold and calculated demeanor hides a passion for problem solving, which makes him quite successful as a detective from the famous Lion's Den detective agency. The best of them wears golden lion mask, to signify their courage and determination in uncovering the hidden.
